{"tid":1990991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［真手足］曾撐方方湖北大學教授 被翻舊帳微博發文悼周梓樂 曾質疑南京大屠殺數字","createTime":"2020-04-27T06:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T08:38:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49fd814ed21756bfdddd72aabeb75fa61d994d06","tid":1990991,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RiG4SE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RiG4SE.png&h=6fb2dda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖北作家方方在 1 月 25 日直至 3 月 25 日，以 60 篇《方方日記》記錄她對武漢封城後，中國抗疫的觀察和看法，包括呼籲外界關注患者遭遇，追究失責官員等，被部分網民指她「抹黑中國抗疫」；事件發酵多日仍未平息，而且有蔓延之勢：跟方方有來往的湖北大學文學院教授、博士生導師梁艷萍，被指去年曾經支持「反送中運動」，悼念去年底在尚德邨停車場墮下身亡的科大學生周梓樂，又質疑南京大屠殺被殺數字的真確性，被網民向校方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯大陸網民表示，梁艷萍過往曾經在微博和微信發表「大逆不道」的帖文，包括在去年 11 月 8 日曾經在微信<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發文表示「周梓樂同學，一路好走」</span></span></strong>，為香港的「反送中運動」表態；去年 10 月 2 日，梁艷萍又在北京舉行「國慶閱兵」後發表短詩，內容提到「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">那一日 巷空 城空，天也空 坦克開進廣場，凛凛威風」、「那一日 曾經的小漁村 學生 孩子 實彈入胸」、「水炮車開上行道 噴出天藍的顏色</span></span></strong>」，被指影射 89 年「六四事件」，以及香港警察在去年 10 月 1 日於荃灣實彈槍傷年輕示威者。<br />\n<br />\n另外，又有網民翻出「漫游者粒子」在 2012 年 12 月 9 日發表的微博，當時的帖文指，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你把三十萬的名單拿出來啊？你說三十萬日本就一定要承認是三十萬，有這樣的道理嗎？」</span></span></span></strong>被指是質疑南京大屠殺官方死亡數字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%96%B9%E6%96%B9%E6%97%A5%E8%A8%98%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%AA%E6%81%AF-%E6%9B%BE%E6%92%90%E6%96%B9%E6%96%B9%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E8%A2%AB%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E5%B8%B3%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%82%BC%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A8%2598%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=4d86a371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A8%2598%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%2F&h=6ff584db\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%96%B9%E6%96%B9%E6%97%A5%E8%A8%98%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%AA%E6%81%AF-%E6%9B%BE%E6%92%90%E6%96%B9%E6%96%B9%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E8%A2%AB%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E5%B8%B3%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%82%BC%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808110d8d63da3f1476b86d1a94e0d4e47737ad3","tid":1990991,"uid":121697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"狙到friend都挖埋出黎<br />\n連坐無極限"},{"pid":"970d5a585d772aff4aff51c57af35a5e3462f3c6","tid":1990991,"uid":324712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"afc9ddf934bf74ccfd0